description	"Rebel Pilot

^2Weaponry:
- Blaster Pistol (1)
- DH-17 Blaster (3)

^8Attributes:
- Reinforcements (1)

^3Abilities:
- Dodge (1) ^3[CS1]

Rebel pilots fly starfighters, light freighters, and atmospheric repulsorlift vehicles for the Alliance Starfighter Corps of the Alliance to Restore the Republic during the Galactic Civil War. Like the rest of the Alliance Military (and unlike the Imperial Navy), they came from a wide variety of species, planets, and backgrounds."